{"tid":2012914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(對家做野啦) 傳擬本月27日恢復二讀國歌法　特首稱已致函內會諮詢","createTime":"2020-05-12T03:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T08:15:14.000Z","uid":104865,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e65a77fbafd28fbb0b7ed04288047b645ef8330","tid":2012914,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:32:02.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥被問到有報道指，當局計劃本月27日在立法會恢復二讀辯論《國歌法》時說，政務司司長等官員已致函立法會內會主席李慧琼，諮詢她有關法案恢復二讀的程序。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥以英文回應提問時說，目前有10項草案，當中兩項包括《國歌法》及《專利(修訂)條例》已被拖延很多時間，她說期望立法會可以優先處理，將這兩項法案恢復二讀辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525635-20200512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525635-20200512.htm&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4e852cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525635-20200512.htm&h=e3009554\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525635-20200512.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2f92a06e17d1fc6f2df96e85405d3c30eb3d2682","tid":2012914,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"56a6e052a728be8d67e41c4820cca8e5a6da91ef","tid":2012914,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc1d2492947512d0817fd872888cb29affa8868b","tid":2012914,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"下次內會幾時"},{"pid":"4f4a9a610de18cc2ab9e93fca704a1033f1e04a5","tid":2012914,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc1d2492947512d0817fd872888cb29affa8868b","tid":2012914,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"下次內會幾時"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"好似一星期一次 上次係8號"},{"pid":"893888aaa9a3fa36eadf2e1e13a131da5e403466"